    {
      "id": "screen-tablet-desc",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 800,
      "y": 190,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 150,
      "text": "Route: /c/vto (home) → journey flow\nTablet device next to the mirror\n\nUser interaction device:\n• Welcome → Session creation\n• QR scan or skip login\n• Selfie + full body capture\n• Catalog browsing & garment selection\n• VTO generation trigger\n• Look review, cart, checkout\n• Gallery sharing via QR",
