    {
      "id": "method2-title",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 560,
      "y": 650,
      "width": 450,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "METHOD 2: Gemini Vision AI (Fallback / Standalone)",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "strokeColor": "#e8590c",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "seed": 51,
      "groupIds": [
        "method2"
      ],
      "boundElements": [],
      "locked": false,
      "roundness": null,
      "link": null,
      "updated": 1778490732387,
      "version": 2,
      "versionNonce": 1755045215,
      "index": "ao",
      "isDeleted": false,
      "frameId": null,
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "METHOD 2: Gemini Vision AI (Fallback / Standalone)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.5625
    },
    {
      "id": "method2-desc",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 560,
      "y": 680,
      "width": 450,
      "height": 230,
      "text": "Backend: analyze-body-measurements edge function\nAI: Gemini (Vertex AI) with vision prompt\n\nTriggered when:\n  • D555 health check fails (not connected)\n  • D555 get-dimensions returns no usable data\n  • Standalone mode (no D555 hardware)\n\nFlow:\n  1. Receives full-body image (base64) from display camera\n  2. Sends to Gemini with PROFILE_AND_MEASUREMENTS_PROMPT\n  3. Gemini analyzes image → returns JSON:\n     - profile: { gender, age_group, body_type }\n     - measurements: { height, chest, waist, hip, ... } in cm\n  4. Converts cm → inches, computes size recommendations\n  5. Saves to vto_sessions.body_measurements\n  6. Broadcasts MEASUREMENTS_READY to tablet\n\nFallback: If Gemini fails → heuristic estimation from height",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "seed": 52,
      "groupIds": [
        "method2"
      ],
      "boundElements": [],
      "locked": false,
      "roundness": null,
      "link": null,
      "updated": 1778490732387,
      "version": 2,
      "versionNonce": 1705143313,
      "index": "ap",
      "isDeleted": false,
      "frameId": null,
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Backend: analyze-body-measurements edge function\nAI: Gemini (Vertex AI) with vision prompt\n\nTriggered when:\n  • D555 health check fails (not connected)\n  • D555 get-dimensions returns no usable data\n  • Standalone mode (no D555 hardware)\n\nFlow:\n  1. Receives full-body image (base64) from display camera\n  2. Sends to Gemini with PROFILE_AND_MEASUREMENTS_PROMPT\n  3. Gemini analyzes image → returns JSON:\n     - profile: { gender, age_group, body_type }\n     - measurements: { height, chest, waist, hip, ... } in cm\n  4. Converts cm → inches, computes size recommendations\n  5. Saves to vto_sessions.body_measurements\n  6. Broadcasts MEASUREMENTS_READY to tablet\n\nFallback: If Gemini fails → heuristic estimation from height",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.1004784688995215
    },
    {
