      "x": 30,
      "y": 1225,
      "width": 360,
      "height": 200,
      "text": "SUPABASE EDGE FUNCTIONS\n\ncreate-session      — New VTO session\nupdate-session      — Patch session fields\ngenerate-virtual-tryon — AI image generation\nanalyze-body-measurements — Gemini body scan\nmeasurement-proxy   — D555 API proxy\nprocess-full-body   — Background removal\ngenerate-video      — AI video from look\nupscale-image       — Image upscaling\nget-gallery         — Public gallery data\ncatalog-upload      — Admin catalog mgmt\nbatch-ghost-mannequin — Garment processing\nvalidate-admin-pin  — Admin auth\nsave-training-data  — ML training data",
