      "y": 1225,
      "width": 360,
      "height": 200,
      "text": "VERTEX AI / GOOGLE CLOUD\n\nVirtual Try-On Model:\n  virtual-try-on-001 (Vertex AI)\n  → Full body + garment → composited image\n\nGemini 2.5 Flash:\n  → Body measurement analysis (vision)\n  → Customer profile detection (gender/age)\n  → Image generation (alternative VTON)\n\nvton-pipeline (Express server):\n  → Orchestrates Vertex AI calls\n  → Image upscaling pipeline\n  → Ghost mannequin processing\n\nPixelBin CDN:\n  → Image/video storage & delivery\n  → Instruction videos, splash assets",
